EXPRESSION: CASE WHEN COALESCE(PXCREATEDATETIME,'') = '' THEN timestamp'1000-01-03 00:00:00.000GMT+7' ELSE to_timestamp(PXCREATEDATETIME,'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss') END
CASE WHEN COALESCE(PXUPDATEDATETIME,'') = '' THEN timestamp'1000-01-03 00:00:00.000GMT+7' ELSE to_timestamp(PXUPDATEDATETIME,'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss') END

CASE WHEN COALESCE(MODIFY_DATE,'') = '' THEN timestamp'1000-01-03 00:00:00.000GMT+7' ELSE (to_timestamp(SUBSTR(MODIFY_DATE,1,4)||'-'||SUBSTR(MODIFY_DATE,5,2)||'-'||SUBSTR(MODIFY_DATE,7,2)||' '|| SUBSTR(MODIFY_DATE,10,2)||':'||SUBSTR(MODIFY_DATE,12,2)||':'||SUBSTR(MODIFY_DATE,14,2)) ) END
